thinner and thinner.

00:07:13.550 --> 00:07:16.190
Literally it was
a wasting disease.

00:07:16.190 --> 00:07:19.160
People would be sent up into
the mountains of Switzerland

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:21.860
to try to recover
